QueryText: What is the recommended dose of fertilizer of chickpea?

Rainfed : 12.5 kg N(30kg Urea) + 25 kg P2O5(150kg SSP)  + 12.5 kg K2O (MOP 20kg) +10 kg S*/ha.
Irrigated : 25 kg N + 50 kg P2O5 + 25 kg K2O + 20 kg S*/ha

b) Soil application of 25 kg ZnSo4/ha under irrigated condition.
